HONG KONG (AP) â€” Venus Williams advanced to the quarterfinals of the Hong Kong Open by beating Wang Yafan of China 6-0, 6-2 Thursday. 
The 35-year-old Williams, a seven-time Grand Slam champion, won the Wuhan Open this month.
